<h3>Show Item Availability</h3><p>Setting this to yes will show the item availability.&nbsp; If you have inventory enabled, this will show if the item is in stock, out of stock, or back order only as well as custom availability.&nbsp; If you have inventory turned off then only the custom availability will be shown.&nbsp; You can select or add availability (i.e. &quot;Ships within 24 hours&quot;) to your products under the settings tab when adding/editing a product.</p>




